            <div class="descr">
                <h2 style="color: #000000;">North County Times</h2>
                <h3>May 17, 2010</h3>
                <p><strong>Re: <a href="/faculty/contactinfo.cfm?detailid=211">Susan Estrich</a></strong></p>
                <p>An op-ed by Prof. Susan Estrich ran stating that the recent Gulf oil spill shows that this isnt the time to reduce government regulation.
</p>
