            <div class="descr">
                <h2 style="color: #000000;">Tax Notes</h2>
                <h3>November 17, 2009</h3>
                <p><strong>Re: <a href="/faculty/contactinfo.cfm?detailid=68912">Edward Kleinbard</a></strong></p>
                <p>Prof. Edward Kleinbards talk at the California State Bar Tax Section's annual meeting was covered. Kleinbard praised the governments response to the financial crisis. "The financial system of this country teetered on the brink of collapse, and if the financial system collapsed, the real economy would have been dragged down with it," Kleinbard said.</p>
